### Shopping Cart API Tests

### 1. Get or Create Cart for User
# Pass user_id as query parameter
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart?user_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Add Item to Cart
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "product_id": 1,
    "variant_id": null,
    "quantity": 2
}

###

### 3. Add Another Item to Cart (with variant)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": 1,
    "product_id": 2,
    "variant_id": 5,
    "quantity": 1
}

###

### 4. Update Cart Item Quantity
# Replace {cartItemId} with actual cart_item_id from previous response
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "quantity": 5
}

###

### 5. Remove Item from Cart
# Replace {cartItemId} with actual cart_item_id
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/items/2

###

### 6. Clear All Items from Cart
# Replace {cartId} with actual cart_id
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/1/clear

###

### 7. Delete Entire Cart
# Replace {cartId} with actual cart_id
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/1

